Layer	Tech	Notes

Frontend	React + Expo + TailwindCSS	responsive learning interface
Backend	Firebase Functions	AI tutor, analytics, mail triggers
Auth	Firebase Auth + Stripe BuzzPay	family & tiered plans
Realtime	Firestore + Storage	progress, badges, avatars
UI	Webflow AutoFlow	visual CMS, push-to-Firebase sync
DevOps	GitHub Actions + Replit Runner	build + deploy automation



